OL,3,CSecond arrest over death of 91-year-
OL,4,Cold woman
OL,6,FPolice investigating the death of a 91-
OL,7,Fyear-old Rotherham woman who was found
OL,8,Fwith serious injuries have made a
OL,9,Fsecond arrest.
OL,11,FOn Thursday 11 September 2025
OL,12,FElizabeth Clark was found with serious
OL,13,Finjuries in her home on Peveril Close,
OL,14,Fin the Kiveton Park area of Rotherham.
OL,16,FOfficers say her bank card was stolen
OL,17,Fthe same day and was used for multiple
OL,18,Ftransactions between 10 and 16
OL,19,FSeptember.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
