PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777641070
OL,3,CSecond arrest over death of 91-year-
OL,4,Cold woman
OL,6,FShe was taken to hospital where she
OL,7,Freceived treatment but passed away as
OL,8,Fa result of her injuries on 12
OL,9,FNovember 2025.
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire Police say a 36-year-
OL,12,Fold man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,13,Fof murder. He has been bailed pending
OL,14,Ffurther enquiries.
OL,16,FHe becomes the second man to be
OL,17,Farrested after a 47-year-old man was
OL,18,Farrested on suspicion of murder in
OL,19,FDecember. He remains on police bail.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
