FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777641070
OL,3,CSecond arrest over death of 91-year-
OL,4,Cold woman
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Adam Watkinson,
OL,7,Fwho is the senior investigating
OL,8,Fofficer and leading the investigation,
OL,9,Fsaid: "It has been nearly six months
OL,10,Fsince the death of Elizabeth and we
OL,11,Fhave been working extensively to find
OL,12,Fanswers for her loved ones.
OL,14,F"Elizabeth was extremely loved by her
OL,15,Ffamily, friends, and was well known in
OL,16,Fthe local community.
OL,18,F"She is missed by many.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
